(122, 126, NULL, NULL, '<div><h5 style=\"margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-family: Poppins, &quot;Odoo Unicode Support Noto&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(52, 58, 64); font-size: 1.09375rem;\">About this item</h5><ul class=\"pl-4 mb-0 d-details\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; list-style-type: disc; line-height: 20px; color: rgb(108, 117, 125); font-family: Roboto, &quot;Odoo Unicode Support Noto&quot;, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 0px !important; padding-left: 1.5rem !important;\"><li class=\" \">Bluetooth Version: 5.0<br></li><li class=\" \">Working Range: 10 Meters<br></li><li class=\" \">Speaker Wattage: 10W*2 (20W)<br></li><li class=\" \">Frequency Response: 150Hz-18KHz<br></li><li class=\"tp-extra-desc\">SNR: 80dB<br></li><li class=\"tp-extra-desc\">Distortion: 10%<br></li><li class=\"tp-extra-desc\">Battery Capacity: 2400mAh/3.7V<br></li><li class=\"tp-extra-desc\">Music Time: About 3.5 Hours<br></li><li class=\"tp-extra-desc\">Talk Time: About 3 Hrs<br></li><li class=\"tp-extra-desc\">Charging Time: About 3.5 Hours<br></li><li class=\"tp-extra-desc\">Charging Interface: Type C<br></li><li class=\"tp-extra-desc\">Weight: 854g<br></li><li class=\"tp-extra-desc\">Size: 255*100*115MM</li></ul></div>', '1 Year', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-08-24 04:51:00', '2024-08-24 04:51:00'),
(123, 127, NULL, NULL, '<div><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">1. This spherical softbox can pop open and be ready to use in mere seconds, allowing you to set up lights, faster. Foldable lantern style, easy to open and close.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">2. The softbox has Bowens mount, with the ability to fit onto any Bowens mount LED heads, speedlights, strobe flash light, monolights fixtures</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">3. With the Lantern will you will be able to produce soft even light wherever your shoots may take you.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">4. The Lantern spreads the light from your LED or Studio Stobe in all directions with a 360 degrees beam angle. Now you can fill an entire space with soft, even light with just a single light source.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">5. Widely used in portrait photography, commercial and advertising photography, children photography, video shooting, micro film shooting, etc.</span><br></div>', 'No', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-08-24 05:18:08', '2024-08-24 06:05:49'),
(124, 128, NULL, NULL, '<div><ul style=\"list-style-type: disc; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.3em; color: rgb(10, 10, 10); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14.4px;\"><li style=\"margin-bottom: 0.6em; margin-left: 1.3em;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Captivating Softbox Lighting</span>&nbsp; Create attractive, soft light and add directional control for portraits, interviews, headshots, live streaming, food photography, vlogging, product photography, and more.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 0.6em; margin-left: 1.3em;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Bowens Mount Compatible</span>&nbsp; The included Bowens mount speed ring gives this softbox full compatibility with an extensive range of LED, strobe, and constant lights.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 0.6em; margin-left: 1.3em;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Rectangular for a Reason</span>&nbsp; The rectangular shape is similar to a window, so it can be used as a general-purpose softbox or to realistically mimic window light.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 0.6em; margin-left: 1.3em;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">For Small or Large Sets</span>&nbsp; The versatile size makes this softbox an excellent choice for key or fill lights, and for use on both small and large sets.</li></ul><div><h1 style=\"color: rgb(221, 153, 51); margin-bottom: 0.5em; text-rendering: optimizespeed; width: 1290px; font-size: 1.7em; line-height: 1.3; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 900;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Nanlite Rectangular Softbox 90X60 with Bowens Mount (35x24in) Overview</span></h1><div>The Nanlite Rectangular Softbox 9060 with Bowens Mount casts attractive, soft light on your subjects and environments and adds directional control. The rectangular shape makes it a great choice for key or fill lights, and its versatile 35 x 24-inch size makes it adaptable for use on both small and large sets. Soft Light, Universally Compatible The Nanlite Rectangular Softbox 9060 is fully compatible with the Nanlite FS-150, FS 200, and FS-300, as well as the Forza 200, 300, 300B, and 500, but it will also fit most lighting instruments that feature the widely popular Bowens mount.</div><div>It is a piece of gear that will be useful for you today and well into the future. It is rectangular for a reason: softboxes come in different shapes to better serve various purposes: round softboxes create natural-looking catchlights in your subjects eyes, asymmetrical softboxes can be useful for side-lighting a person who is standing. The Nanlite Rectangular Softbox 9060 is similar to the size and shape of a window, so it can be used as a standard, general purpose softbox, but it can also be used to realistically mimic window light. Diffusion Included, Travel Ready A custom-fitted diffusion panel is included with the Nanlite Rectangular Softbox 9060, and the interior has a reflective silver color that intensifies the output of your light. It also comes with a carrying bag so youre always ready to travel to your shooting locations.</div></div></div>', 'No', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-08-24 06:38:16', '2024-08-28 05:17:56'),
